    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Motif resembling ribbon, often in swirling, windblown forms, or in the form of a tied bow, with long streamer ends, seen in used on furniture, metalwork, ceramics, and textiles.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
